  "content": "<p data-pid=\"8H2UkkF9\">参考官方文档：</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//docs.ankiweb.net/editing.html%3Fhighlight%3Dtemplate%23customizing-fields\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Adding/Editing - Anki Manual</a><p data-pid=\"uARpwwKl\">首先，先进入浏览，找一个最基础的正面、反面模板：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-dd1b27cff1de5e190920b3a0ad4fddf0_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1860\" data-rawheight=\"1234\" data-original-token=\"v2-dd1b27cff1de5e190920b3a0ad4fddf0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-65a4516b42462698d965e3e03967a23a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1860\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-dd1b27cff1de5e190920b3a0ad4fddf0_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1860&#39; height=&#39;1234&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1860\" data-rawheight=\"1234\" data-original-token=\"v2-dd1b27cff1de5e190920b3a0ad4fddf0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-65a4516b42462698d965e3e03967a23a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1860\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-dd1b27cff1de5e190920b3a0ad4fddf0_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-dd1b27cff1de5e190920b3a0ad4fddf0_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"dPJ1iZp2\">点击「字段…」，会出现以下界面：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8fd2a2eac7ee78b9de579d3ca4d34712_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1490\" data-rawheight=\"1032\" data-original-token=\"v2-8fd2a2eac7ee78b9de579d3ca4d34712\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8b7dbe1e410eaf25b87f1e059e945e4d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1490\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8fd2a2eac7ee78b9de579d3ca4d34712_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1490&#39; height=&#39;1032&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1490\" data-rawheight=\"1032\" data-original-token=\"v2-8fd2a2eac7ee78b9de579d3ca4d34712\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8b7dbe1e410eaf25b87f1e059e945e4d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1490\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8fd2a2eac7ee78b9de579d3ca4d34712_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8fd2a2eac7ee78b9de579d3ca4d34712_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"6NdeyxUU\">通过「重命名」和「添加」，可以实现题主想要的效果：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4cdf50e4be63416d3edd6881afb1345e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"966\" data-rawheight=\"760\" data-original-token=\"v2-4cdf50e4be63416d3edd6881afb1345e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-6f7b4470d92128d4fda6e02eeae593b2_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"966\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-4cdf50e4be63416d3edd6881afb1345e_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;966&#39; height=&#39;760&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"966\" data-rawheight=\"760\" data-original-token=\"v2-4cdf50e4be63416d3edd6881afb1345e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-6f7b4470d92128d4fda6e02eeae593b2_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"966\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-4cdf50e4be63416d3edd6881afb1345e_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4cdf50e4be63416d3edd6881afb1345e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"MjUAMwUA\">点「save」保存，就可以了，效果如下：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-80518747c3a29f4bd04efb6f69058f89_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1500\" data-rawheight=\"1126\" data-original-token=\"v2-80518747c3a29f4bd04efb6f69058f89\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-f7bedf53ce5becab6aec8a50587dae4b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1500\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-80518747c3a29f4bd04efb6f69058f89_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1500&#39; height=&#39;1126&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1500\" data-rawheight=\"1126\" data-original-token=\"v2-80518747c3a29f4bd04efb6f69058f89\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-f7bedf53ce5becab6aec8a50587dae4b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1500\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-80518747c3a29f4bd04efb6f69058f89_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-80518747c3a29f4bd04efb6f69058f89_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"Hbb1xLv0\">希望解决了题主的问题。</p><hr/><p data-pid=\"Hx7u3RPP\">更多 Anki 相关的教程，请参阅：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/61564332\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-acfa8f607f2d3c74ba5c660c3ab25df0_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1161\" data-image-height=\"500\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：Anki 教程(电子书)与 B 站 Ankidroid 教程(视频)快速通道</a><p></p>",
